# Template for hibiki/dart_defines.env (which is gitignored).
# Copy to dart_defines.env and fill in your own values.
#
# SECURITY (HBK-AUDIT-072): a --dart-define value is compiled as a plaintext
# constant into the APK, so GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET ships to every user and
# is trivially extractable. Google issues installed-app OAuth client secrets as
# NON-confidential by design, so this is acceptable ONLY for the installed-app
# (PKCE) flow — do NOT treat it as a real secret. If a truly confidential
# secret is ever needed, move that flow to a backend. Rotate any secret that
# was committed/distributed.
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET=your-non-confidential-installed-app-secret
